{"tid":51253,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎巴打討論 謝絕A0","createTime":"2016-12-23T05:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T07:35:01.000Z","uid":40984,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a52f096791aca385308e6c7c78bb0ff52695842","tid":51253,"uid":40984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"我好愛我女朋友，但日子越耐覺得佢越煩，成日做埋啲港女野，有時真係成個啊媽咁。當我話佢煩激嬲佢個時，佢唔理我，玩失蹤，但我竟然唔係由得佢，而係騰晒雞，驚佢離開我。好啦，終於俾我氹返，但無耐，我又開始覺得佢煩，重重覆覆。我係咪好犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n唔要啲咩哪有女既巴打黎留言 真心想討論係咪大部份既巴打都係咁既心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c2c2e4bae1399eeba6ff256ddf2fa86d8deda0","tid":51253,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"a0留名"},{"pid":"142635d21af2b71798988f6bceb8f3b310243826","tid":51253,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6ab594a1e2e995d675d844d1b2d0120dcc989c4","tid":51253,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359aa2204f4f492d0a3e73d7bf9cce7a8a73a794","tid":51253,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab0f122758d09ee196f6e56f83ae51057f5997d4","tid":51253,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"當係情趣啦<br />\n睇下你地一個願打一個願捱邊方先攰嫁嫁啫"},{"pid":"35d00de51455c248855d6e412630b75efcb78451","tid":51253,"uid":67898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"我都覺得女友煩嫁 成日都有唔同原因話我 例如懶呀唔浪漫唔準備禮物 仲要成日嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkg